  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "55 injured in the struggle to the hospital",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Hospital sources say that 55 people who suffered various accidents while coming to Colombo for the protest have been admitted to the Colombo National Hospital.",
        "Hospital sources say that there are four women among them.",
        "The sources said that the condition of some people was taken to hospital."
